query:
INSERT INTO labelAssociations (productId, labelCode, batch, expiryDate, createdAt, updatedAt, associatedBy, sessionId)
SELECT 
  pwi.productId,
  '83420722D08LA129' as labelCode,
  pwi.batch,
  pwi.expiryDate,
  NOW(),
  NOW(),
  1 as associatedBy,
  1 as sessionId
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
WHERE pwi.waveId = 3 AND pwi.productSku = '834207'
LIMIT 1;
